thread.title_full: Best Storage Henderson reviewed by Yvonne Lipman

author: Yvonne Lipman
title: Yvonne Lipman
text: Highly recommend this place for storage needs. They were honest, upfront, and had what I needed on short notice. The facility is neat and clean and the management was fantastic. I am not one to write reviews often but with outstanding service like this, I had to express my recommendation. Thanks for helping me out and being so fun and professional.
